tion/high-precision finite difference program COACH verifies the\nreliability and capability of the proposed algorithm. A comparison of running\ntimes illustrates that the algorithm proposed in this paper is significantly\nfaster than the full three-dimensional algorithm in terms of computational\nspeed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 03:11:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 03:17:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2022 08:28:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 03:35:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-14"}
