reases as the density and neutrino energy\nincrease, which is consistent with the result obtained in the Brussels-Montreal\nSkyrme (BSk17 and BSk18) models at saturation density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 08:55:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 13:57:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-09"}
